Police said in a statement they have been monitoring the illegal drug dealings that were taking place at the house in Rustenburg for some time."On Monday 6 March 2017 at about 07:30 members of K9 Phokeng raided the house. They recovered cocaine concealed inside the pillows in the couple's bed."The pair aged 32 and 43 are due to appear at Rustenburg Magistrate Court soon facing charges of possession of drugs.